  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Review existing endpoint patterns in Program.cs</step>
    <step order="2">Create response DTO record: OpenLinksResponse { DesktopUrl, WebUrl, MimeType }</step>
    <step order="3">Add GET /api/open-links endpoint with driveItemId query parameter</step>
    <step order="4">Add parameter validation - return 400 if driveItemId is null/empty</step>
    <step order="5">Inject ISpeFileStore or GraphServiceClient to retrieve DriveItem</step>
    <step order="6">Call Graph API to get DriveItem by ID</step>
    <step order="7">Extract webUrl and file.mimeType from DriveItem response</step>
    <step order="8">Call DesktopUrlBuilder.FromMime(webUrl, mimeType)</step>
    <step order="9">Return OpenLinksResponse with all URLs</step>
    <step order="10">Add error handling - return 404 if item not found</step>
    <step order="11">Add .RequireAuthorization() to endpoint</step>
    <step order="12">Add .WithTags("OpenLinks") for Swagger grouping</step>
    <step order="13">Test endpoint manually with valid driveItemId</step>
